description: Commands to manage endpoints in the specified workspace.

commands.name: az databricks workspace outbound-endpoint list
commands.summary: List the list of endpoints that VNET Injected Workspace calls Azure Databricks Control Plane. You must configure outbound access with these endpoints. For more information, see https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/databricks/administration-guide/cloud-configurations/azure/udr.
